          Description

Class Summary
M2MQualityConfiguration Stores the configurations made within a M2M Quality eclipse launch configuration plus a list of language configurations describing language-specific properties important for executing measurements for the respective language itself.
M2MQualityConfiguratorPlugin This class activates the M2M Quality measurement configuration plug-in.
 

Package de.upb.m2m.quality.configurator Description

Constitutes the core of the M2M Quality framework. The framework is mainly based on a work flow that parses each language of interest to create a language-specific AST model and transforming it to a quality metrics model. The package itself includes classes for managing the plug-in's life-cycle (M2MQualityConfigurationPlugin class) and storing configuration properties for the work flow (M2MQualityConfiguration class). The "jobs" subpackage includes the implementations of the work flow consisting of several jobs.
